<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="403" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="10.[1404,2611,294,729]" pageId="10" pageNumber="403">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1406,1752,610,643]" pageId="10" pageNumber="403">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Abundance of the Apennine Shrew is low everywhere.
</paragraph>
